:0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:54:04.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"03d28d4db24eff7686ddc551d8fb45ed2c46b1e2","tid":1738259,"uid":81434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:10:00.000Z","msg":"人呢仆街"},{"pid":"bbc8aba18a05ef8fc6b91cb8ff037b7d1a9a0d15","tid":1738259,"uid":81434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:11:55.000Z","msg":"又話冇戰術post"},{"pid":"33af82557a18b63b350282ed70332f293898c12e","tid":1738259,"uid":81434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:12:16.000Z","msg":"打咁大段嘢比人當傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34735c2eae6067ac0b2f578ab79a32ac37fe907e","tid":1738259,"uid":81434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:12:36.000Z","msg":"大家入嚟屌吓我都好😭"},{"pid":"7de12887afc6e79b06c7c42a3f963d23fcd806f0","tid":1738259,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:15:18.000Z","msg":"我覺得當RB向再加嘅時候<br />\n後面嘅應該睇下洗唔洗拆咁啲<br />\n好多時塞死晒啲人"},{"pid":"73d2e3b4be1fe76fd79395268f8ffeb15a21d6f4","tid":1738259,"uid":121408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:21:30.000Z","msg":"推！！！磚rb一set錯位真係害死人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個kick親，後面都會遭殃"},{"pid":"c47afb6b8cb26660c57c8e3e70231ac689f5a16a","tid":1738259,"uid":204133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:29:06.000Z","msg":"好多人冇野做就瘋狂亂set rb，kick死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67ccba231ebcc2223c1d912b1b95d7dee7b2995c","tid":1738259,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:39:03.000Z","msg":"唔岩 橫街都係我地散<br />\n依加對家直射衝前 仲有車衝 <br />\n無人有勇氣反打<br />\n大家只係橫散 跑到有氣既人就再下個街口 都係橫散<br />\n<br />\n你set橫街就即係封埋自己 頂死自己主路線真勇武<br />\n<br />\n應該封路線側兩街尾 eg砵蘭街 西洋菜街<br />\n同橫街盡頭 eg 上海街<br />\n咁先有縱深"},{"pid":"45d71dcbfbd3478550ebe1aba51ae8eb33b554fa","tid":1738259,"uid":328471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T23:26:01.000Z","msg":"咁講法 係咪應該開幾條rb小隊 連住幾個哨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我地已經時常處於缺人缺物資嘅狀態<em><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></em>"}]}